      <title>受补贴热潮影响，中国 11 月汽车销量有望增长 18%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-november-car-sales-seen-surging-18-on-subsidy-rush</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于汽车制造商加大折扣，且买家争相在政府以旧换新补贴结束前享受补贴，中国 11 月份汽车销量可能大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-november-car-sales-seen-surging-18-on-subsidy-rush</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>修订后的 PMI 显示，英国企业勉强避免萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-businesses-narrowly-avoid-contraction-revised-pmi-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[修订后的采购管理数据显示，由于对工党政府首份预算中加税的担忧日益加剧，英国私营部门 11 月份表现为 13 个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-businesses-narrowly-avoid-contraction-revised-pmi-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全文：韩国央行行长谈戒严、利率和经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/in-full-bok-governor-on-martial-law-rates-economy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镛讨论了总统尹锡烈周二晚间颁布戒严令后的市场反应。在接受彭博社记者哈斯琳达·阿敏采访时，他表示，尽管政治混乱，但央行不太可能降息。他还对政府应对危机的能力表示有信心，并表示地缘政治紧张局势和全球贸易不确定性是更大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/in-full-bok-governor-on-martial-law-rates-economy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:26:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
