      <title>纳米比亚连续第三次下调基准利率至 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/namibia-lowers-key-rate-for-third-time-in-row-to-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着通胀率降至三年多来的最低水平，纳米比亚央行连续第三次下调基准利率。]]></description>
