    <item>
      <title>经合组织称，若不进一步提高税收，英国的财政立场将难以为继</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-fiscal-stance-unsustainable-without-more-tax-rises-oecd-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织上调了对英国的经济增长预测，并表示英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯需要进一步提高税收，以使公共财政保持可持续的基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/uk-fiscal-stance-unsustainable-without-more-tax-rises-oecd-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织警告称，世界正面临贸易紧张和债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/pre-trump-world-is-seen-menaced-by-dangers-from-trade-to-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织表示，全球经济面临的贸易紧张、战争、债务问题等风险不断增加，可能威胁到过去几年全球经济的“显著韧性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/pre-trump-world-is-seen-menaced-by-dangers-from-trade-to-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克央行行长表示将很快停止降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/czech-central-bank-chief-says-rate-cuts-likely-to-be-halted-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克央行行长阿莱斯·米歇尔表示，捷克央行可能在不久的将来停止货币宽松政策，并在一段时间内维持利率不变，以使通胀回到目标水平，这刺激了克朗的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/czech-central-bank-chief-says-rate-cuts-likely-to-be-halted-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
